import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Sometimes we deviate from strict schema.org for the sake of brevity, clarity or developer convenience.  We have tried to note each such instance in our examples, please let us know if you see a deviation we haven't documented.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"types"}}>{`Types`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"new-types"}}>{`New Types`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-organization.md"}}>{`RealEstateOrganization`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-office.md"}}>{`RealEstateOffice`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-agent.md"}}>{`RealEstateAgent`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"identifier"}}>{`identifier`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`  Identifier in REflex is a context specific Map<name,value> useful for matching objects across related systems`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`# Reflex identifier Map
type: Thing
identifier:
    '@context': 'https://context.yodata.io/hsf/reflex'
    ContactID: 1234
    
# strict schema.org equivalent (a bit too wordy)

type: 'https://schema.org/Thing'
identifier: [
    '@context': 'https://context.yodata.io/yodata/hsf/reflex'
    type: PropertyValue
    name: ContactID
    value: 1234
]
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
